title: Google\Cloud\Talent\V4beta1\ProfileEvent
name: ProfileEvent
description:
An event issued when a profile searcher interacts with the application that implements Cloud Talent Solution.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.talent.v4beta1.ProfileEvent
